Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.31,0:23:06.27,EDCNCHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}儘管這絕望 不竭不衰
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.03,0:23:15.95,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}狂った時計　刻む命
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.03,0:23:15.95,EDCNCHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}失準的時鐘 記錄著生命
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.03,0:23:19.83,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}こぼれてく記憶の砂
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.03,0:23:19.83,EDCNCHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}散落滿地的記憶之砂
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.91,0:23:23.71,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}芽生えた想いまで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.91,0:23:23.71,EDCNCHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}以及萌生的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.79,0:23:28.67,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}ねえ　こんなに呆気なく
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.79,0:23:28.67,EDCNCHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}你看 卻是那麼輕易
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.67,0:23:35.97,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}消えてしまうの
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.67,0:23:35.97,EDCNCHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}消失殆盡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.01,0:23:37.22,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}I wish I was there
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.01,0:23:37.22,EDCNCHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}我希望能與你同在
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.26,0:23:39.30,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}Oh,please don't let me die
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.26,0:23:39.30,EDCNCHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}請不要讓我離開
